      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for someone seeking dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and straightforward utility, but it still offers solid everyday potential with the right expectations. A sensible choice for commuting, a first project, or an inexpensive backup vehicle.",
