      "description": "Honest little car being sold as a budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a tidy-up project. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it has plenty of usable life left for the right buyer and could be a great fit for a first car, spare runaround, or weekend fixer-upper. Priced fairly for what it is, and I\u2019m happy to answer questions so you know exactly what you\u2019re coming to see.",
